# qodana-js — Qodana Ultimate for JS/TS (image name = repoName). Feed code QDJS, PUBLIC feed: this
# `.env` OMITS QD_DISTRIBUTION_FEED and relies on lib/dist.dockerfile's public-feed default. The FIRST
# DHI-language-base image: QD_BASE_IMAGE is the dhi.io/node base (Node + Yarn PRE-BAKED), so there is
# NO NODE_MAJOR and no node toolchain. The node base ships a `node` user at uid 1000, so the qodana user
# shifts to 1001 via QODANA_UID/QODANA_GID — passed as COMPOSE BUILD ARGS (like clang's CLI_BASE_STAGE),
# NOT `.env` keys: dockerfile-x emits each INCLUDE_ARGS key as an `ARG NAME="val"` default, which the
# base fragment's own `ARG QODANA_UID=1000` (declared later, after the INCLUDE_ARGS block) would CLOBBER
# back to 1000 — verified empirically. A `--build-arg` always wins over a redeclared default, so the
# override lives in compose.yaml. eslint is pinned in lib/toolchain/eslint/package.json (renovate-
# tracked), NOT here. Pins are the concrete values in docs/phase-0-decisions.md; EnvContractTest asserts
# byte-identity for QD_VERSION/QD_BUILD/QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE and the node base digest.
QD_LINTER_SLUG=qodana-js
QD_VERSION=2026.1
QD_BUILD=261.25882
QD_RELEASE_TYPE=release
QD_PRODUCT_INFO_CODE=WS
QD_BASE_IMAGE=dhi.io/node:22-debian13-dev@sha256:e2df7b939a83d8825e7f5fcd8c9b54ecf53fd40565e5523d71a0442c7a098f10
CLI_BINARY=qodana
CLI_VERSION=2026.2
CLI_OS=linux
CLI_ARCH=amd64
TINI_VERSION=v0.19.0
TINI_ARCH=amd64
TINI_SHA256=93dcc18adc78c65a028a84799ecf8ad40c936fdfc5f2a57b1acda5a8117fa82c
